{"tid":270354,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"啲咩中大舊生老鬼真係笑大人個口","createTime":"2017-06-04T09:31:30.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-04T16:52:31.000Z","uid":5195,"like":27,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"99d608622435f137113d3c1b178e2eef713cf1ac","tid":270354,"uid":5195,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T09:31:30.000Z","msg":"啲咩中大舊生老鬼真係笑大人個口<br />\n今屆學生會佢地又無份投票，講撚到自己早知唔投佢地、射佢地埋牆咁款<br />\n人地又無阻止啲老嘢去跟支聯會悼念<br />\n一句講晒: 香港係因為當時邊班人既決定而變到今時今日咁既情況？<br />\n係度笑人地屌人地，問人地有咩行動<br />\n如果唔係佢地果代人既決定同行動，香港年青人洗依家咁？"},{"pid":"824012a631c3a59f64b9d98f2ddecc88351783cb","tid":270354,"uid":54733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T09:36:07.000Z","msg":"其實D老鬼嘈乜春<br />\n<br />\n學生會關佢地咩事<br />\n<br />\n畢左業都要嘈生哂"},{"pid":"e95860fed959f6067f7c2e51ba0458694682fe86","tid":270354,"uid":1082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T09:40:07.000Z","msg":"人地都開論壇講六四，仲想點，係咪年年同你出去唱自由花<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n想唱k , 自己開間k 房囉，何必要出去捐錢比個盤數唔清唔楚既組織<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17c64232c06af1a03c5684ed16f582cf6c703288","tid":270354,"uid":100016,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T09:46:02.000Z","msg":"爭取民主但完全唔尊重民主"},{"pid":"494596d9ad07195f2ba59590e870be56c3281502","tid":270354,"uid":54927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T09:50:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>爭取民主但完全唔尊重民主</blockquote><br />\n啱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港人最撚獨裁"},{"pid":"c09fe942c97d4a259144c4a48ac20988663f7754","tid":270354,"uid":56453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T09:53:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實D老鬼嘈乜春<br />\n<br />\n學生會關佢地咩事<br />\n<br />\n畢左業都要嘈生哂</blockquote><br />\n佢地係有權有自由唔同意中大學生會方針同想法<br />\n但係唔講重以為人地學生會殺撚晒佢地全家，個個都仆出黎狂屌"},{"pid":"892ad6a85684ba88fbd342e8ef00005a7c0028b2","tid":270354,"uid":12599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T10:12:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>其實D老鬼嘈乜春<br />\n<br />\n學生會關佢地咩事<br />\n<br />\n畢左業都要嘈生哂</blockquote><br />\n佢地係有權有自由唔同意中大學生會方針同想法<br />\n但係唔講重以為人地學生會殺撚晒佢地全家，個個都仆出黎狂屌</blockquote><br />\n斷支聯會米路,更係狂屌"},{"pid":"1b0a9aced2750938bb76ba7981d56dff29df8ffe","tid":270354,"uid":11753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T10:13:57.000Z","msg":"有幾多個認真睇曬篇文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1bd1da3ccf7bb8e26b83283344d5c914aeb02097","tid":270354,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T10:58:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01e269bc8bc4f2b88caa92a8aafeb62609172d2f","tid":270354,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T12:06:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d757354f4eda900f08d5db048a187a711e4f192","tid":270354,"uid":35870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T12:08:12.000Z","msg":"老鬼都係老屎忽文化之一！"},{"pid":"128e3ee9fa7f51bfdc90635a83473ed3cb9e2b67","tid":270354,"uid":92301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T12:09:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>爭取民主但完全唔尊重民主</blockquote><br />\n泛民<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"080ab61ea1cb3efec719749d00bb9a6d8bbef926","tid":270354,"uid":54959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T12:10:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>爭取民主但完全唔尊重民主</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5b884f687efbe4227a93406f40fbfcfe88ee9df","tid":270354,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T15:01:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3790cb9399e458bb338e1517253c9e3a213272e8","tid":270354,"uid":9348,"li